title: r/Entitledparents Let My Kids Steal, Or I'm Calling The Cops On You!
description:
r/Entitledparents The spoiled parents in today's video are absolutely nuts! A bunch of kids keep breaking into a junk yard to steal stuff from the cars. So, the owner puts up an electric fence, which ENRAGES the parents. How dare they endanger their precious little brats while they're stealing from OP!? Believe it or not, they actually have the audacity to call the cops on OP!

Watch on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R0XbA7TJ2kw
